    coro,
    ellmer,
    htmltools,
    promises,
    rlang,
    shiny,
    uuid
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
